duties:
Provide one-on-one or group support to students in beginning and intermediate French courses. The duties of this position include:
• helping beginning and intermediate students practice their French pronunciation, develop their speaking skills, understand essential grammatical concepts and improve their vocabulary;
• guiding informal and formal conversations in French to help intermediate students improve their spontaneous interactions in French;
• reviewing material learned in class and helping students with questions about grammar and syntax;
• Other duties, as appropriate


Provide 2 hour/ week availability. Duties are completed in-person at UTSC from September 2024 - December 2024.
Schedule to be determined in conjunction with Program Coordinator


Note: The number of hours are an estimate and are tentative pending enrolment numbers.
